OL,3,CTribute paid to 'loving and warm
OL,4,Cindividual' allegedly murdered in
OL,5,CAbergavenny
OL,7,FA man allegedly murdered in Wales was
OL,8,Fa "beloved son" who "never thought
OL,9,Ftwice about helping others", his
OL,10,Ffamily has said.
OL,12,F24-year-old Idris Squires, from
OL,13,FAbergavenny, had a "huge circle of
OL,14,Ffriends" and was the "most kind,
OL,15,Floving and warm individual you could
OL,16,Fever wish to meet", according to a
OL,17,Ffamily statement issued through Gwent
OL,18,FPolice.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@[O]uD@TOUvD@HO]vD@VOUxD@RO]
