OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1779825947
OL,3,CTribute paid to 'loving and warm
OL,4,Cindividual' allegedly murdered in
OL,5,CAbergavenny
OL,7,FMr Squires was found with life-
OL,8,Fthreatening injuries on Old Hereford
OL,9,FRoad, Abergavenny, at around 6:15am on
OL,10,F15 May.
OL,12,FHe later died in hospital.
OL,14,FHis family described him as the "most
OL,15,Fkind, loving and warm individual you
OL,16,Fcould ever wish to meet."
OL,18,F"He never thought twice about helping
OL,19,Fothers, young or old, he had the
OL,20,Finstinct to do the right thing.
OL,26,@zD@AOU
