OL,3,CTribute paid to 'loving and warm
OL,4,Cindividual' allegedly murdered in
OL,5,CAbergavenny
OL,7,F"We are proud of his gift of organ
OL,8,Fdonation ` that he elected to be on
OL,9,Fthe donor register, speaks volumes for
OL,10,Fthe man he was.
OL,12,F"Although we are overwhelmed by the
OL,13,Fgrief of losing such a wonderful young
OL,14,Fman, we take comfort in the memory of
OL,15,Fthe love, laughter and kindness that
OL,16,Fhe shared with those he met.
OL,18,F"He will be forever in our thoughts
OL,19,Fand in our hearts."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU{D@SO]
